g.title: Sheet.231
g.desc: User Case: Developing Package Foo and Package Foo is dependen...
g.text: User Case: Developing Package Foo and Package Foo is dependent on Package Bar THEN:· The developer clones the SCM repository for package Foo under the workspace-root/ directory· If using a released version of Bar, · The developer mounts (e.g. orc mount bar-main-1.1.4) the desired released version of Bar.· If using an unreleased snapshot of Bar, · The developer clones the SCM repository for package Bar under the workspace-root/ directory · The developer mounts local snapshot of Bar (e.g. orc mount bar)
